cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the development of an application for the quantitative analysis of multichannel 5-D microscopy images, which involves image segmentation, tracking, and lineage analysis. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), which are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of GPU for visualization tasks, which could fall under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
